@node legal "How to use and distribute East"
	East is (c) @{"Rainald March" link author}.
	East is FREEWARE. There are no restrictions. Use it as a
	preparator of an agressive war, or even as a salesman of a
	German life insurance. I shan't complain.
	Feel free to redistribute, improve and extend the program, and
	to use the algorithm for your own purposes.
	The doc file must follow the program without changes, except for
	the version not(d)e. Cat file and template are needed for use.
	Distributors of Digita are allowed to supply the program with
	any documentation, or without it.
@endnode

@node install "Installation"
	Sorry, no Installer script. Simply copy the program file, the
	catalog file and the template file into any directory.
	Cat file and template are supplied in English, German and Spanish.
@endnode

@node version "Version"
	Original release, no changes performed.
@endnode

@node author "Author"
	Rainald March
